---
description: Vercel deployment & environment hygiene for Shopify apps.
globs:
  - vercel.json
  - .vercel/**/*
  - src/**/*
alwaysApply: true
---

Rules:
- Configure env vars in Vercel (SHOPIFY_API_KEY, SHOPIFY_API_SECRET, SCOPES, APP_URL, WEBHOOK_SECRET if separate).
- Never commit secrets. Use Vercel project-level envs and pull locally via `vercel env pull`.
- Health endpoint `/api/health` for uptime checks.
- Enable edge cache only for static assets and public pages; never cache embedded app screens with session data.